Source: ev3dev-mocks
Section: devel
Priority: standard
Maintainer: David Lechner <david@lechnology.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cmake, libasound2-dev, pandoc, pkg-config
Standards-Version: 3.9.7
Homepage: https://www.ev3dev.org
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/ev3dev/ev3dev-mocks.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/ev3dev/ev3dev-mocks

Package: ev3dev-mocks
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, umockdev (>= 0.11.1-1ev3dev2~), libasound2-plugin-ev3dev
Description: Fake udev and ALSA sound utility for ev3dev
 Tools for faking ev3dev hardware for unit testing.
 .
 This package contains umockdev configuration files for simulating ev3dev
 Linux kernel drivers. It also includes an ALSA plugin for simulating
 the ev3dev sound driver.

Package: libasound2-plugin-ev3dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fake udev and ALSA sound utility for ev3dev
 Tools for faking ev3dev hardware for unit testing.
 .
 This package contains umockdev configuration files for simulating ev3dev
 Linux kernel drivers. It also includes an ALSA plugin for simulating
 the ev3dev sound driver.
 .
 This package provides the ALSA plugin.
